{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"auto-build-json-files-on-hg-pull-push\">\n<span id=\"autobuild\"></span><h1>Auto-build JSON files on <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">hg</span> <span class=\"pre\">pull/push</span></tt><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#auto-build-json-files-on-hg-pull-push\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>If you use <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://selenic.com/mercurial/\">Mercurial (hg)</a>, you can update\nyour documentation automatically each time you push to your web server (or if\nyou pull from another server to your web server).</p>\n<p>To do that, open your repository\u2019s <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">.hg/hgrc</span></tt> in your favorite editor and add\nthe following lines to it:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-cfg\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">[hooks]</span>\n<span class=\"na\">changegroup</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s\">/path/to/your/python path/to/manage.py updatedoc -b &lt;project&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n<p>Now, each time the repository is modified via a pull or push command, the\ndocumentation on your Django site will be updated automatically.</p>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": false, "title": "Auto-build JSON files on <tt class=\"docutils literal docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">hg</span> <span class=\"pre\">pull/push</span></tt>", "sourcename": "autobuild.txt", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "autobuild", "next": {"link": "../change_appearance/", "title": "Change your documentation&#8217;s appearance"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["py-modindex", "Python Module Index", "", "modules"], ["change_appearance", "Change your documentation&#8217;s appearance", "N", "next"], ["quickstart", "Quickstart Guide", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Auto-build JSON files on <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">hg</span> <span class=\"pre\">pull/push</span></tt></a></li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../quickstart/", "title": "Quickstart Guide"}, "metatags": ""}